title: With a sickening thud, I hit the concrete... Was this my last bike ride to work?
text: Recreational Cycling With a sickening thud, I hit the concrete... Was this my last bike ride to work? Lying in a crumpled heap after coming off my bicycle in London, I soon realised I was one of the lucky ones The scene of a fatal crash at Bank junction, London, earlier this year Photo: Tolga Akmen/LNP
